\fs24\insrsid10094515\charrsid11357524  }{\fs24\insrsid9261759 The display shows }{\fs24\insrsid10094515\charrsid11357524 one byte per location}{\fs24\insrsid9261759  of the byte-addressable memory}{\fs24\insrsid10094515\charrsid11357524 
